'''Battle of Borleias''' was a [[holodocumentary]] about the [[Battle of Borleias (Yuuzhan Vong War; Second)|Siege of Borleias]] during the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]]. Narrated by [[Wolam Tser]] and recorded by [[Tam Elgrin]], the holo portrayed the forces under [[General/Legends|General]] [[Wedge Antilles/Legends|Wedge Antilles]]&mdash;and the rest of the [[New Republic Defense Force/Legends|New Republic Defense Force]] in general&mdash;in a positive manner, boosting the sagging morale that the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] had experienced during the [[Battle of Coruscant (Yuuzhan Vong War)|Battle]] of [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. The holo was a huge success, and helped increase enlistment in the Defense Force.

